des:
Mystic Rose Magick is a metaphysical gift and supply shop located in the southern tier of upstate new York where you'll find candles, crystals, incense, essential oils. magical herbs, books, tarot, oracle decks, divination tools, figurines, gemstone jewelry and so much more. We also have the area's most trusted and reliable psychic readers and Tarot Masters every Saturday. Schedule a Reiki session or class from our experienced Reiki Grand master Kristina. We also offer Hypnosis for change as well as past-life regression. You'll also want to take a look at our upcoming schedule of workshops and classes, too. People come to Mystic Rose Magick for the fabulous energy and because they know they’ll find what they’re looking for on our shelves - and if they don’t, we’ll help them find it. We're practitioners too and strive to provide the best quality products available. Stop by our upper loft sanctuary and see for yourself. We're at 31 Main Street #201 in Addison. We're making' magic, upstairs beyond the purple door!
